# Local Rust build artifacts
rust/target/
rust/settings.json

# Local binary/package artifacts
*.exe
*.scr
*.msi
*.pdb

# Overlay assets. The directory is local-only by default; the
# counter-ignored files below are the curated pack that ships in the
# MSI and survives clones.
#
#   matrisaver-default.png — the project's own brand mark, owned
#       outright, zero third-party rights.
#   The other two — shipped by explicit owner decision. See the
#       v0.2.1 commit message and CHANGELOG for the rights posture
#       (stock-vector filename suggests a Shutterstock comp; the
#       WhatsApp image is owner-supplied).
#
# neo.png is deliberately NOT counter-ignored: it is a film still,
# © Warner Bros., and the MIT LICENSE cannot grant rights to it. It
# stays local-only for dev testing. A WBD Clip & Still licensing
# request would be the path to ever shipping it.
assets/overlays/*
!assets/overlays/README.md
!assets/overlays/matrisaver-default.png
!assets/overlays/WhatsApp Image 2026-02-15 at 10.38.31.jpeg
!assets/overlays/stock-vector-all-seeing-eye-of-god-in-triangle-sacred-symbol-in-a-stylized-triangles-vector-monochrome-2189023981.jpg

# Source-resolution branding assets (4K PNG / 6K JPG from OpenArt) stay
# local; only the downscaled web variants in assets/branding/ are tracked.
assets/assets/

# Runtime/validation artifacts are local-only by default.
artifacts/*
!artifacts/readme.md
